<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
 <head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Jma Welcome Email</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <!-- Responsive stuff -->
  <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True">
  <meta name="MobileOptimized" content="320">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  	
  <link href="http://www.jqueryscript.net/css/jquerysctipttop.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
  <link href="css/jma.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.0.3.min.js"></script> 
  <script src="js/jquery.progressTimer.js"></script>


    <!-- HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML5 elements. All other JS at the end of file. -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="js/html5shiv.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  <style>
  h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, legend, p {
  color: #5e605d;
}
  </style>
</head>
<body>  
    <div class="thumbnail" style="width: 600px; margin-left: 10%; margin-top: 2%;">
       <a href="http://www.jodymichael.com"><img src="http://www.jodymichael.com/filebin/images/logo.png" alt="<= @reference %>"  style="display: block; margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;"></a>
        <br>
          <img src="http://www.jodymichael.com/filebin/images/dotted-border-img.png" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <br>
      <p>Hi <%=@name%>,</p>
      <p><%= @greeting1%><b><%= @appt_date_formatted %></b>,<%= @greeting2%> </p>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <p><b><u>Location</u></b></p>
          <p>4860 N. Paulina</p>
          <p>Chicago, IL 60640</p>
          <p></p>
          <p>This is a residential building. Please let yourself in the middle door at the top of the stairs. Street parking is available.</p>
       </div>
     </div>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
           <% if @appt_date_formatted  %>
              <p><b><u>Date and Time</u></b></p>
              <p>We will begin on <b><%= @appt_date_formatted %>, at <%= @appt_start %> Sharp!</b>  Please be on time.  The training will end at or before 4:00 pm. </p>
              <br>
              <p><b>If you are late, you will not be admitted to the workshop. Please do not disrupt us.</b></p>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p><b><u>Food</u></b></p>
            <p>Please reply to this e-mail with your potbelly lunch order no later than noon on the Friday before the workshop.  The everyday menu is located <a href="http://www.potbelly.com/Food/OurMenu.aspx?subPage=Sandwiches" style="color: #8bc129;">here</a>, and the soup menu by day is listed <a href="http://www.potbelly.com/Shops/ShopLocator.aspx#&&ss=False&lat=41.9703133&sid=238&lng=-87.663045&p=1&b=0&sl=False&d=0&s=60640&f=0&v=True" style="color: #8bc129;">Here</a> .  Please, if you are ordering a sandwich, make sure you provide all details needed to order (size, type of bread, toppings, etc.).  If we don’t hear back from you by noon on Friday, we’ll order a turkey sandwich for you.  We will provide coffee in the morning, and drinks and snacks through-out the day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p><b><u>Heads-up</u></b></p>
            <p><%= @text3 %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p><b><u>The Icebreaker</u></b></p>
            <p><%= @text4 %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
              <p><b><u>Pre-work</u></b></p>
            <p><%= @closing_text %></p> 
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>Kelly</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    
     </div>
    <br>
</div>

</body>
</html>
